OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FHundreds of people working in the UK's
OL,8,Fbars, restaurants, hotels and
OL,9,Fcampsites are suspected to be victims
OL,10,Fof modern slavery, some with debts as
OL,11,Fhigh as #30,000 after being "lured" by
OL,12,Fpromises of a better life, according
OL,13,Fto a new report.
OL,15,FThe charity Unseen said similar abuses
OL,16,Fevident in the care sector in recent
OL,17,Fyears are now becoming apparent in the
OL,18,Fhospitality industry, with its
OL,19,Fhelpline recording a sharp rise in
OL,20,Fpotential victims linked to the
OL,21,Fskilled worker visa route.
