OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FLast year, 75 modern slavery potential
OL,8,Fvictims in the hospitality sector were
OL,9,Freportedly on these visas, up from
OL,10,Fjust one in 2023.
OL,12,FOverall, between January 2024 and June
OL,13,F2025, there were 485 potential victims
OL,14,Freported to the Unseen helpline
OL,15,Fworking in food and drink venues,
OL,16,Fwhich can include takeaways and
OL,17,Fcatering companies as well as bars and
OL,18,Frestaurants, and 85 in holiday
OL,19,Faccommodation such as hotels, motels,
OL,20,Fcampsites and holiday lets.
