OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThese included people on skilled
OL,8,Fworker visas, and those on other kinds
OL,9,Fof visas, or workers for which visa
OL,10,Finformation was not made clear to the
OL,11,Fhelpline.
OL,13,FThe report said: "The same
OL,14,Fcharacteristics that have been evident
OL,15,Fin modern slavery in the care sector
OL,16,Fsince 2022 have now become apparent in
OL,17,Fhospitality, with migrant workers
OL,18,Fexperiencing many of the same abuses
OL,19,Fat the hands of their employers.
