OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Key themes relate to a large
OL,8,Fdisparity between what is promised to
OL,9,Fa worker and the reality once they
OL,10,Farrive in the UK. Illegal fees are
OL,11,Fcharged in exchange for visas and
OL,12,Fcertificates of sponsorship; workers
OL,13,Fare commonly housed on site or in
OL,14,Faccommodation provided by their
OL,15,Femployer; workers are threatened with
OL,16,Fhaving their visas revoked or being
OL,17,Fdeported."
