OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FFigures published earlier this year
OL,8,Fsuggested thousands of care workers
OL,9,Fhave come to the UK in recent years
OL,10,Funder sponsors whose licences were
OL,11,Flater revoked, in estimates suggesting
OL,12,Fthe scale of exploitation in the
OL,13,Fsystem.
OL,15,FJustine Carter, deputy chief executive
OL,16,Fat Unseen, said the hospitality sector
OL,17,Fis showing "the same characteristics"
OL,18,Fof exploitation first seen in the UK
OL,19,Fcare sector in 2022.
