OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FShe said: "There is a large disparity
OL,8,Fbetween what is promised to workers
OL,9,Fand the reality once they arrive in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,F"Many are charged illegal fees, forced
OL,13,Finto substandard housing, and
OL,14,Fthreatened with deportation if they
OL,15,Fspeak up."
