OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe report said that while employers
OL,8,Fare required to cover costs relating
OL,9,Fto recruitment, this is not always
OL,10,Fwhat happens, with "many employers"
OL,11,Fnot only demanding migrant workers pay
OL,12,Ffor their visas and certificates of
OL,13,Fsponsorship, but also charging them
OL,14,F"exorbitant fees".
OL,16,FThe helpline has had examples of
OL,17,Fhospitality workers being illegally
OL,18,Fcharged between #4,000 and #30,000 by
OL,19,Ftheir employers for so-called visa
OL,20,Ffees, with average debts at around
OL,21,F#18,271.
