OL,3,CHundreds of modern slavery victims
OL,4,Cwork in UK's bars and hotels, charity
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FIndian nationals were most commonly
OL,8,Freported in modern slavery situations
OL,9,Fin hospitality, accounting for 40%
OL,10,Foverall, followed by Bangladeshi
OL,11,Fnationals, making up 13%.
OL,13,FWhile numbers of British nationals
OL,14,Fwere low, the UK was in the top four
OL,15,Facross 2024 and the first half of
OL,16,F2025, with 17 modern slavery potential
OL,17,Fvictims in hospitality across the two
OL,18,Fyears.
