OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMigration minister Mike Tapp said:
OL,8,F"Those who abuse our immigration
OL,9,Fsystem must face the strongest
OL,10,Fpossible consequences.
OL,12,F"We will not hesitate to ban companies
OL,13,Ffrom sponsoring workers from overseas
OL,14,Fwhere this is being done to undercut
OL,15,FBritish workers and exploit vulnerable
OL,16,Fstaff.
OL,18,F"My message to unscrupulous employers
OL,19,Fis clear: these shameful practices
OL,20,Fwill not be tolerated."
